{"tid":627782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"猝死工人遺妻兒 獨生子：我會好好照顧媽咪","createTime":"2018-04-13T09:13:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T05:10:38.000Z","uid":12618,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"bff1f47f391f4f5d3137b2259cf401dd9524f910","tid":627782,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T09:13:05.000Z","msg":"昨日在尖沙嘴香港藝術館暈倒、送院不治的47歲電工羅帶聖，兒子在親友陪同下到殮房辦認屍手續。羅子稱，父親向來身體壯健「傷風感冒都好少」，事出突然，母子倆措手不及，母親更傷心過度要入院治理。即將面對大學畢業試的羅子強忍淚水，向亡父承諾「會好好照顧媽咪」。<br />\n<br />\n今晨9時許，死者兒子在伯父等親友陪同下，到葵涌殮房辦理認屍手續，其中女親友都傷心落淚。死者獨生子阿生稱，父親在三兄弟中排最細，身體一向壯健，年青時更在游泳比賽中捧盃，平日「傷風感冒都好少」，醫生也沒說明死因，要待剖屍結果。<br />\n<br />\n阿生續稱，父親做電工散工，月薪約3萬元，在肇事地盤返工約三個月，每周工作6天。由於家住屯門，清晨6點便要起床預備，早出晚歸。據工友向他們稱，昨日父親工作期間突然表示不適，將他扶到一旁休息，約5分鐘後便告暈倒。在場有人替他急救，惜送院後不治。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿生在浸會大學讀商科，今年四年級最後一年，他痛心父親未能目睹他戴四方帽便告離世。母親是家庭主婦，昨日聞悉丈夫猝死，哭得死去活來，要送院治理，目前還在醫院留醫。阿生坦言，父親是經濟支持，現時母子倆頓失依靠，十分徬徨。不過，他明白要收拾心情，既要考畢業試，也要肩負照顧媽媽的責任。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"299932c6b038d82a12ab243a4f2ef99364cd726b","tid":627782,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T09:14:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180413&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58067594\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180413%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58067594&d=wKwydBehBStME9sSWVBXME%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=073be33c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180413%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58067594&h=117ac282\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180413&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58067594</a>"},{"pid":"6de3dc615162aff3cef0fdc09e24a25a7d3ecd4a","tid":627782,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T09:16:25.000Z","msg":"電工都咁辛苦，仆街香港。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c52c299c3d65aa41bd89d3cc757860ff54148af0","tid":627782,"uid":31314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T09:23:32.000Z","msg":"阿仔真男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27503bdfc6d57290a0177e3369500991f660297e","tid":627782,"uid":12618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c52c299c3d65aa41bd89d3cc757860ff54148af0","tid":627782,"uid":31314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T09:23:32.000Z","msg":"阿仔真男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T09:30:51.000Z","msg":"媽咪咁樣 唔堅強好難行落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c77e01dfe31acf4e86b115e18a95a5698898a84d","tid":627782,"uid":12618,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6de3dc615162aff3cef0fdc09e24a25a7d3ecd4a","tid":627782,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T09:16:25.000Z","msg":"電工都咁辛苦，仆街香港。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T09:31:34.000Z","msg":"用人用到盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc0d568fcbf1cf0cee888cd434b9b1bc10b474f4","tid":627782,"uid":168534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T09:46:27.000Z","msg":"福都冇機會享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f1ecdce2ec6d431413ec422236a24182a4698a","tid":627782,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc0d568fcbf1cf0cee888cd434b9b1bc10b474f4",